---
layout: base.njk
title: Improvlore - Bangalore
showCustomEvents: false
requiresEvents: true
---

<div class="events-root">

  {# Hero answers "who are you / is this for me / where do I go" for a new
     visitor, while keeping a fast path into events. The featured card shows
     the single next upcoming event of any type, with a copy fallback if
     nothing is scheduled so the hero never renders half-empty. #}
  {% set heroNext = filters.nextEvent(events, showCustomEvents) %}

  <section class="home-hero" aria-labelledby="hero-heading">
    <div class="home-hero-intro">
      <p class="home-hero-eyebrow">Improv in Bangalore and beyond, since 2022</p>
      <p class="fun-shout" aria-hidden="true"><span class="fun-f">F</span><span class="fun-u">U</span><span class="fun-n">N</span></p>
      <h1 class="home-hero-heading" id="hero-heading">Live theatre, made up on the spot.</h1>
      <p class="home-hero-lede">No script, no second take. We build shows from your suggestions, then never do them again. Come watch, jump into a jam, or learn it yourself.</p>
      <div class="home-hero-cta">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/events/">See what's on</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    {% if heroNext %}
    <a class="home-hero-next" href="{{ filters.eventPermalink(heroNext) }}">
      <img class="home-hero-next-poster" src="{{ filters.eventImage(heroNext) }}" alt="{{ heroNext.title }} poster" loading="eager">
      <span class="home-hero-next-body">
        <span class="home-hero-next-kicker">Up next</span>
        <span class="home-hero-next-title">{{ filters.workshopName(heroNext.title) }}</span>
        {% set heroSessions = filters.eventSessions(heroNext.title) %}
        <span class="home-hero-next-blurb">{{ filters.formatDay(heroNext.event_starts_at) }}, {{ filters.formatDayNum(heroNext.event_starts_at) }} {{ filters.formatMonth(heroNext.event_starts_at) }} at {{ filters.formatTime(heroNext.event_starts_at) }}{% if heroSessions and heroSessions.dates and heroSessions.dates.length > 1 %} <span class="home-hero-next-tag">+{{ heroSessions.dates.length - 1 }} more dates</span>{% endif %}</span>
      </span>
    </a>
    {% endif %}
  </section>

  <section class="page-section" aria-labelledby="section-start">
    <h2 class="section-heading" id="section-start">New Here? Start Anywhere</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">However you like to play, there's a way in. We just want you to find joy in play again.</p>

    <ul class="book-offer-list about-paths">
      <li>
        <a class="about-path-link" href="/events/?type=show">
          <strong>Watch a show</strong>
          <p>Sit back and let us build a one-time-only show from your suggestions. No pressure to do a thing.</p>
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a class="about-path-link" href="/events/?type=jam">
          <strong>Play at a jam</strong>
          <p>Our open, beginner-friendly sessions. Jump in, mess around, meet people. No experience needed.</p>
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a class="about-path-link" href="/events/?type=workshop">
          <strong>Take a workshop</strong>
          <p>Learn by doing, at a pace that's kind to first-timers. A guided room where it's safe to try.</p>
        </a>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <p class="book-cta-line">Pricing and venue are listed on each event, so you always know before you go.</p>
  </section>

  <p class="yesand-shout" aria-hidden="true"><span class="yesand-yes">WHIM</span><span class="yesand-and">SY</span></p>

  <section class="page-section" aria-labelledby="section-about">
    <h2 class="section-heading" id="section-about">Who We Are</h2>

    <div class="about-intro">
      <p class="about-lede">We make up theatre on the spot, with no script and no second take. Around since 2022, building stories that never existed before and never will again, and letting a room feel its way through them together.</p>
    </div>

    <p class="more-line">
      Weekly jams, workshops, and shows built live from whatever the room gives us.
      <a href="/about/">Read our story →</a>
    </p>

    <p class="more-line">
      Since 2024 we've packed our shows off to improv festivals across Asia: Singapore, Vietnam, Manila, Hong Kong.
      <a href="/festivals/">See where we've been →</a>
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="page-section" aria-labelledby="section-shows">
    <h2 class="section-heading" id="section-shows">Shows We Are Known For</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Built live from what the room gives us, so no two are the same. A few of the formats we keep coming back to.</p>

    <ul class="about-shows" aria-label="Signature show formats">
      {% for show in signatureShows %}
      <li>
        <a class="about-show-card" href="{{ show.url }}">
          <div class="about-show-poster-wrap">
            <img class="about-show-poster" src="{{ show.image }}" alt="{{ show.title }} poster" loading="lazy">
            {% if show.festival %}<span class="festival-badge" title="A format we tour to international festivals">International format</span>{% endif %}
          </div>
          <div class="about-show-body">
            <strong>{{ show.title }}</strong>
            <span>{{ show.blurb }}</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="page-section page-section-info" aria-labelledby="section-more">
    <h2 class="section-heading" id="section-more">More From Us</h2>

    <a class="corporate-banner" href="/for-teams/">
      <span class="corporate-banner-text">
        <strong>We bring improv to workplaces too.</strong>
        Custom shows and team workshops, shaped around your team.
      </span>
      <span class="corporate-banner-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
    </a>

    
  </section>

</div>
